title: Ben Shepherd - Baron Robber.mp3
description:
Ben Shepherd of Soundgarden will release his debut solo album 'In Deep Owl' in August. 

The collection of songs was recorded in the industrial neighborhoods of Georgetown and Interbay in Seattle, WA and was produced by Dave French, Ben Shepherd, Chad MacMurray, and Nathan Yaccino.

If you like the song buy the album on August 27th, 2013. 

Enjoy & Seed.
